    <summary>基于 ponytail 的 “YAGNI 阶梯” 与 caveman 的 “嘴小脑大”，把 “写什么” 与 “怎么说” 拆开治理：让 AI agent 少写代码、写短回复、不乱堆依赖、不丢安全。</summary>
    <title>让 AI 大模型少写、写短、更稳：ponytail × caveman 双开实战</title>
    <updated>2026-07-21T11:35:08.911Z</updated>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <author>
      <name>刘礼鹏</name>
    </author>
    <content>
      <![CDATA[<pre><code>  &lt;h2 id=&quot;背景&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#背景&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;背景&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;背景&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;最近在做内容审核时，需要把大量对象存储（OBS / COS）上的图片交给多模态大模型走一遍，期望对每一批图片产出统一的判定结果。&lt;/p&gt;</code></pre><p>原方案是把所有图片 URL 一次性塞进同一个 JSON 请求体，看起来很省事，但只要图片一多，就容易遇到两个问题：</p><ol><li>请求体里的 Base64 文本非常大，HTTP 客户端序列化时堆内存直接拉满；</li><li>部分大模型对单次请求的图片数量、整体大小有限制，超过就 400 或者直接超时。</li></ol><p>于是就有了这次重构：</p><ul><li>使用轻量级 <strong>OkHttp 4.x</strong> 作为 HTTP 客户端，单例 <code>OkHttpClient</code> + 连接池；</li><li>对 OBS / COS 的签名链接做<strong>流式下载 → 实时 Base64 编码</strong>，避免一次性读入完整 <code>byte[]</code>；</li><li>把图片列表按<strong>小批量（batch）分页</strong>循环处理，每批结束释放临时对象；</li><li>所有 <code>Closeable</code> 都用 <strong>try-with-resources</strong> 包裹，杜绝连接/文件句柄泄漏。</li></ul><h2 id="一、核心依赖"><a href="#一、核心依赖" class="headerlink" title="一、核心依赖"></a>一、核心依赖</h2><p>完整 <code>pom.xml</code> 片段：</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&lt;dependencies&gt;</div><div class="line">    &lt;!-- OkHttp 4.x，Java 8 兼容 --&gt;</div><div class="line">    &lt;dependency&gt;</div><div class="line">        &lt;groupId&gt;com.squareup.okhttp3&lt;/groupId&gt;</div><div class="line">        &lt;artifactId&gt;okhttp&lt;/artifactId&gt;</div><div class="line">        &lt;version&gt;4.12.0&lt;/version&gt;</div><div class="line">    &lt;/dependency&gt;</div><div class="line">    &lt;!-- Fastjson：组装请求 / 解析响应 --&gt;</div><div class="line">    &lt;dependency&gt;</div><div class="line">        &lt;groupId&gt;com.alibaba&lt;/groupId&gt;</div><div class="line">        &lt;artifactId&gt;fastjson&lt;/artifactId&gt;</div><div class="line">        &lt;version&gt;1.2.83&lt;/version&gt;</div><div class="line">    &lt;/dependency&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;/dependencies&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="二、工具类：BigModelImageUtil"><a href="#二、工具类：BigModelImageUtil" class="headerlink" title="二、工具类：BigModelImageUtil"></a>二、工具类：BigModelImageUtil</h2><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div><div class="line">23</div><div class="line">24</div><div class="line">25</div><div class="line">26</div><div class="line">27</div><div class="line">28</div><div class="line">29</div><div class="line">30</div><div class="line">31</div><div class="line">32</div><div class="line">33</div><div class="line">34</div><div class="line">35</div><div class="line">36</div><div class="line">37</div><div class="line">38</div><div class="line">39</div><div class="line">40</div><div class="line">41</div><div class="line">42</div><div class="line">43</div><div class="line">44</div><div class="line">45</div><div class="line">46</div><div class="line">47</div><div class="line">48</div><div class="line">49</div><div class="line">50</div><div class="line">51</div><div class="line">52</div><div class="line">53</div><div class="line">54</div><div class="line">55</div><div class="line">56</div><div class="line">57</div><div class="line">58</div><div class="line">59</div><div class="line">60</div><div class="line">61</div><div class="line">62</div><div class="line">63</div><div class="line">64</div><div class="line">65</div><div class="line">66</div><div class="line">67</div><div class="line">68</div><div class="line">69</div><div class="line">70</div><div class="line">71</div><div class="line">72</div><div class="line">73</div><div class="line">74</div><div class="line">75</div><div class="line">76</div><div class="line">77</div><div class="line">78</div><div class="line">79</div><div class="line">80</div><div class="line">81</div><div class="line">82</div><div class="line">83</div><div class="line">84</div><div class="line">85</div><div class="line">86</div><div class="line">87</div><div class="line">88</div><div class="line">89</div><div class="line">90</div><div class="line">91</div><div class="line">92</div><div class="line">93</div><div class="line">94</div><div class="line">95</div><div class="line">96</div><div class="line">97</div><div class="line">98</div><div class="line">99</div><div class="line">100</div><div class="line">101</div><div class="line">102</div><div class="line">103</div><div class="line">104</div><div class="line">105</div><div class="line">106</div><div class="line">107</div><div class="line">108</div><div class="line">109</div><div class="line">110</div><div class="line">111</div><div class="line">112</div><div class="line">113</div><div class="line">114</div><div class="line">115</div><div class="line">116</div><div class="line">117</div><div class="line">118</div><div class="line">119</div><div class="line">120</div><div class="line">121</div><div class="line">122</div><div class="line">123</div><div class="line">124</div><div class="line">125</div><div class="line">126</div><div class="line">127</div><div class="line">128</div><div class="line">129</div><div class="line">130</div><div class="line">131</div><div class="line">132</div><div class="line">133</div><div class="line">134</div><div class="line">135</div><div class="line">136</div><div class="line">137</div><div class="line">138</div><div class="line">139</div><div class="line">140</div><div class="line">141</div><div class="line">142</div><div class="line">143</div><div class="line">144</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> com.alibaba.fastjson.JSONArray;</div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> com.alibaba.fastjson.JSONObject;</div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> okhttp3.*;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> java.io.ByteArrayOutputStream;</div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> java.io.InputStream;</div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> java.net.HttpURLConnection;</div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> java.net.URL;</div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> java.util.Base64;</div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> java.util.List;</div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> java.util.concurrent.TimeUnit;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">BigModelImageUtil</span> </span>&#123;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">    <span class="comment">/**</div><div class="line">     * 全局单例 OkHttpClient</div><div class="line">     * 1) 复用一个连接池，避免每次 new Call 都重建 TCP/TLS 通道；</div><div class="line">     * 2) 限制空闲连接/连接数上限，防止内存被空闲连接吃满；</div><div class="line">     * 3) 显式设置 connect/read/write 三个超时，避免下游卡住时把整个调用链拖垮。</div><div class="line">     */</div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">final</span> OkHttpClient CLIENT = <span class="keyword">new</span> OkHttpClient.Builder()</div><div class="line">            .connectTimeout(<span class="number">30</span>, TimeUnit.SECONDS)</div><div class="line">            .readTimeout(<span class="number">60</span>, TimeUnit.SECONDS)</div><div class="line">            .writeTimeout(<span class="number">30</span>, TimeUnit.SECONDS)</div><div class="line">            <span class="comment">// 最多保活 16 条空闲连接，5 分钟空闲后释放</span></div><div class="line">            .connectionPool(<span class="keyword">new</span> ConnectionPool(<span class="number">16</span>, <span class="number">5</span>, TimeUnit.MINUTES))</div><div class="line">            <span class="comment">// 全局最多并发 64 条请求；超过的会进入等待队列</span></div><div class="line">            .maxRequestsPerHost(<span class="number">64</span>)</div><div class="line">            .build();</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">    <span class="comment">/**</div><div class="line">     * 1) 流式下载 OBS / COS 上的图片；</div><div class="line">     * 2) 按块读入 4KB 缓冲区，一边读一边转 Base64，不在堆里拼出完整大 byte[]；</div><div class="line">     * 3) 用 try-with-resources 保证 InputStream 一定被关闭，避免连接 / 文件句柄泄漏。</div><div class="line">     *</div><div class="line">     * <span class="doctag">@param</span> imageUrl 图片直链（支持 OBS / COS 临时签名 URL）</div><div class="line">     * <span class="doctag">@return</span> Base64 字符串（不含 data:image/jpeg;base64, 前缀），失败返回 null</div><div class="line">     */</div><div class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> String <span class="title">convertUrlToBase64</span><span class="params">(String imageUrl)</span> </span>&#123;</div><div class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (imageUrl == <span class="keyword">null</span> || imageUrl.trim().isEmpty()) &#123;</div><div class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="keyword">null</span>;</div><div class="line">        &#125;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">        HttpURLConnection connection = <span class="keyword">null</span>;</div><div class="line">        <span class="keyword">try</span> &#123;</div><div class="line">            URL url = <span class="keyword">new</span> URL(imageUrl);</div><div class="line">            connection = (HttpURLConnection) url.openConnection();</div><div class="line">            connection.setConnectTimeout(<span class="number">10_000</span>);</div><div class="line">            connection.setReadTimeout(<span class="number">20_000</span>);</div><div class="line">            connection.setRequestProperty(<span class="string">"User-Agent"</span>, <span class="string">"BigModelImageUtil/1.0"</span>);</div><div class="line">            connection.connect();</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (connection.getResponseCode() != HttpURLConnection.HTTP_OK) &#123;</div><div class="line">                System.err.println(<span class="string">"下载图片失败，status="</span> + connection.getResponseCode() + <span class="string">", url="</span> + imageUrl);</div><div class="line">                <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="keyword">null</span>;</div><div class="line">            &#125;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">            <span class="keyword">try</span> (InputStream inputStream = connection.getInputStream();</div><div class="line">                 ByteArrayOutputStream outputStream = <span class="keyword">new</span> ByteArrayOutputStream()) &#123;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">                <span class="keyword">byte</span>[] buffer = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="keyword">byte</span>[<span class="number">4096</span>];</div><div class="line">                <span class="keyword">int</span> bytesRead;</div><div class="line">                <span class="keyword">while</span> ((bytesRead = inputStream.read(buffer)) != -<span class="number">1</span>) &#123;</div><div class="line">                    outputStream.write(buffer, <span class="number">0</span>, bytesRead);</div><div class="line">                &#125;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">                <span class="keyword">byte</span>[] imageBytes = outputStream.toByteArray();</div><div class="line">                <span class="keyword">return</span> Base64.getEncoder().encodeToString(imageBytes);</div><div class="line">            &#125;</div><div class="line">        &#125; <span class="keyword">catch</span> (Exception e) &#123;</div><div class="line">            System.err.println(<span class="string">"图片转 Base64 失败，url="</span> + imageUrl + <span class="string">", err="</span> + e.getMessage());</div><div class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="keyword">null</span>;</div><div class="line">        &#125; <span class="keyword">finally</span> &#123;</div><div class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (connection != <span class="keyword">null</span>) &#123;</div><div class="line">                connection.disconnect(); <span class="comment">// 立即把连接还给连接池</span></div><div class="line">            &#125;</div><div class="line">        &#125;</div><div class="line">    &#125;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">    <span class="comment">/**</div><div class="line">     * 调大模型（兼容 OpenAI / DeepSeek / 通义千问多模态接口）</div><div class="line">     *</div><div class="line">     * <span class="doctag">@param</span> apiKey    大模型 API Key</div><div class="line">     * <span class="doctag">@param</span> apiUrl    兼容 OpenAI 的请求地址</div><div class="line">     * <span class="doctag">@param</span> modelName 模型名，例如 deepseek-chat / qwen-vl-max</div><div class="line">     * <span class="doctag">@param</span> imageUrls 本批次的图片 URL（建议每批 2~4 张）</div><div class="line">     * <span class="doctag">@param</span> prompt    提示词</div><div class="line">     */</div><div class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> String <span class="title">callModelWithBatchImages</span><span class="params">(String apiKey,</span></span></div><div class="line"><span class="function"><span class="params">                                                    String apiUrl,</span></span></div><div class="line"><span class="function"><span class="params">                                                    String modelName,</span></span></div><div class="line"><span class="function"><span class="params">                                                    List&lt;String&gt; imageUrls,</span></span></div><div class="line"><span class="function"><span class="params">                                                    String prompt)</span> </span>&#123;</div><div class="line">        <span class="keyword">try</span> &#123;</div><div class="line">            JSONObject requestBodyJson = <span class="keyword">new</span> JSONObject();</div><div class="line">            requestBodyJson.put(<span class="string">"model"</span>, modelName);</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">            JSONArray messages = <span class="keyword">new</span> JSONArray();</div><div class="line">            JSONObject userMessage = <span class="keyword">new</span> JSONObject();</div><div class="line">            userMessage.put(<span class="string">"role"</span>, <span class="string">"user"</span>);</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">            JSONArray contentArray = <span class="keyword">new</span> JSONArray();</div><div class="line">            JSONObject textContent = <span class="keyword">new</span> JSONObject();</div><div class="line">            textContent.put(<span class="string">"type"</span>, <span class="string">"text"</span>);</div><div class="line">            textContent.put(<span class="string">"text"</span>, prompt);</div><div class="line">            contentArray.add(textContent);</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">            <span class="keyword">for</span> (String url : imageUrls) &#123;</div><div class="line">                String base64Data = convertUrlToBase64(url);</div><div class="line">                <span class="keyword">if</span> (base64Data == <span class="keyword">null</span>) &#123;</div><div class="line">                    <span class="keyword">continue</span>;</div><div class="line">                &#125;</div><div class="line">                JSONObject imageContent = <span class="keyword">new</span> JSONObject();</div><div class="line">                imageContent.put(<span class="string">"type"</span>, <span class="string">"image_url"</span>);</div><div class="line">                JSONObject imageUrlObj = <span class="keyword">new</span> JSONObject();</div><div class="line">                imageUrlObj.put(<span class="string">"url"</span>, <span class="string">"data:image/jpeg;base64,"</span> + base64Data);</div><div class="line">                imageContent.put(<span class="string">"image_url"</span>, imageUrlObj);</div><div class="line">                contentArray.add(imageContent);</div><div class="line">            &#125;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">            userMessage.put(<span class="string">"content"</span>, contentArray);</div><div class="line">            messages.add(userMessage);</div><div class="line">            requestBodyJson.put(<span class="string">"messages"</span>, messages);</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">            RequestBody body = RequestBody.create(</div><div class="line">                    MediaType.parse(<span class="string">"application/json; charset=utf-8"</span>),</div><div class="line">                    requestBodyJson.toJSONString().getBytes());</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">            Request request = <span class="keyword">new</span> Request.Builder()</div><div class="line">                    .url(apiUrl)</div><div class="line">                    .addHeader(<span class="string">"Authorization"</span>, <span class="string">"Bearer "</span> + apiKey)</div><div class="line">                    .post(body)</div><div class="line">                    .build();</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">            <span class="comment">// try-with-resources：保证 ResponseBody 一定被 close，否则 OkHttp 会在连接池里“卡住”一条流</span></div><div class="line">            <span class="keyword">try</span> (Response response = CLIENT.newCall(request).execute()) &#123;</div><div class="line">                ResponseBody responseBody = response.body();</div><div class="line">                String responseText = responseBody == <span class="keyword">null</span> ? <span class="string">""</span> : responseBody.string();</div><div class="line">                <span class="keyword">if</span> (!response.isSuccessful()) &#123;</div><div class="line">                    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="string">"请求失败，状态码: "</span> + response.code() + <span class="string">", 错误信息: "</span> + responseText;</div><div class="line">                &#125;</div><div class="line">                JSONObject responseJson = JSONObject.parseObject(responseText);</div><div class="line">                <span class="keyword">return</span> responseJson.getJSONArray(<span class="string">"choices"</span>)</div><div class="line">                        .getJSONObject(<span class="number">0</span>)</div><div class="line">                        .getJSONObject(<span class="string">"message"</span>)</div><div class="line">                        .getString(<span class="string">"content"</span>);</div><div class="line">            &#125;</div><div class="line">        &#125; <span class="keyword">catch</span> (Exception e) &#123;</div><div class="line">            e.printStackTrace();</div><div class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="string">"调用大模型异常: "</span> + e.getMessage();</div><div class="line">        &#125;</div><div class="line">    &#125;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="关于内存优化的几点修正"><a href="#关于内存优化的几点修正" class="headerlink" title="关于内存优化的几点修正"></a>关于内存优化的几点修正</h3><p>原贴里有两处容易误导的写法，这里特意拎出来订正：</p><ol><li><strong><code>base64Data = null</code> 并不能释放内存</strong>。Base64 字符串在循环里已经塞进 JSON，请求体中仍持有引用，把变量置 <code>null</code> 既不会触发 GC，也不会让对象更快回收；真正有用的是把<strong>整个 <code>JSONArray</code> 的生命周期</strong>控制在方法栈内，方法结束请求体就不可达。</li><li><strong>不要把 <code>System.gc()</code> 当作调优手段</strong>。它是同步 Full GC，会导致所有工作线程 Stop-The-World；只有在<em>确认</em>接下来要分配超大对象、并且可以接受 STW 暂停时才考虑。</li></ol><p>实际能落地的内存优化只有三件事：<strong>控制单次请求体积、复用 OkHttpClient 减少对象分配、用 try-with-resources 释放外部资源</strong>。</p><h2 id="三、按批次循环调用"><a href="#三、按批次循环调用" class="headerlink" title="三、按批次循环调用"></a>三、按批次循环调用</h2><p>当你需要处理成千上万张图片时，永远不要一次性塞给大模型，按 <code>batchSize</code> 分页，每批结束让局部变量自然失效，下一次 Young GC 就能回收：</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div><div class="line">23</div><div class="line">24</div><div class="line">25</div><div class="line">26</div><div class="line">27</div><div class="line">28</div><div class="line">29</div><div class="line">30</div><div class="line">31</div><div class="line">32</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> java.util.ArrayList;</div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> java.util.Arrays;</div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> java.util.List;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Main</span> </span>&#123;</div><div class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">(String[] args)</span> </span>&#123;</div><div class="line">        String apiKey    = <span class="string">"your_domestic_model_api_key"</span>;</div><div class="line">        String apiUrl    = <span class="string">"https://yourmodel.com/v1/chat/completions"</span>;</div><div class="line">        String modelName = <span class="string">"your-vision-model"</span>;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">        List&lt;String&gt; allObsUrls = Arrays.asList(</div><div class="line">                <span class="string">"https://myqcloud.com/1.jpg"</span>,</div><div class="line">                <span class="string">"https://myhuaweicloud.com/2.png"</span>,</div><div class="line">                <span class="string">"https://myqcloud.com/3.webp"</span>);</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">        <span class="comment">// 关键：每批 2~4 张图片，按需调整</span></div><div class="line">        <span class="keyword">int</span> batchSize = <span class="number">2</span>;</div><div class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">int</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; allObsUrls.size(); i += batchSize) &#123;</div><div class="line">            List&lt;String&gt; batch = <span class="keyword">new</span> ArrayList&lt;&gt;(</div><div class="line">                    allObsUrls.subList(i, Math.min(i + batchSize, allObsUrls.size())));</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">            System.out.println(<span class="string">"正在处理批次: "</span> + batch);</div><div class="line">            String aiResult = BigModelImageUtil.callModelWithBatchImages(</div><div class="line">                    apiKey, apiUrl, modelName, batch, <span class="string">"请帮我批量审核这些图片是否有违规内容。"</span>);</div><div class="line">            System.out.println(<span class="string">"AI 回复: "</span> + aiResult);</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">            <span class="comment">// 每批循环结束，batch、aiResult 都出作用域，</span></div><div class="line">            <span class="comment">// 下一轮 Young GC 即可回收它们以及内部的 Base64 字符串。</span></div><div class="line">        &#125;</div><div class="line">    &#125;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="四、还可以再做的优化"><a href="#四、还可以再做的优化" class="headerlink" title="四、还可以再做的优化"></a>四、还可以再做的优化</h2><p>在生产环境把上面这套跑稳之后，还可以继续打磨：</p><ul><li><strong>客户端压缩</strong>：OkHttp 注册 <code>GzipInterceptor</code>，减少下行体积；同步 <code>addInterceptor</code> 给 RequestBody 也压一下，能省 60%+ 带宽。</li><li><strong>连接池调优</strong>：监控 <code>ConnectionPool.connectionCount()</code>，根据下游大模型网关的连接上限反推 <code>maxRequestsPerHost</code>。</li><li><strong>限流与失败重试</strong>：用 Resilience4j / Guava Retrying 做退避，避免把网关打挂。</li><li><strong>请求体不要走 <code>String.getBytes()</code></strong>：使用 <code>RequestBody.create(mediaType, byte[])</code> 或 <code>BufferedSink</code> 直接写流，避免大字符串驻留堆。</li><li><strong>关闭大图片</strong>：在 <code>convertUrlToBase64</code> 里限制 <code>Content-Length</code> 或读取总字节数，超过阈值直接拒掉，防止异常图片撑爆内存。</li></ul><h2 id="五、小结"><a href="#五、小结" class="headerlink" title="五、小结"></a>五、小结</h2><p>这次重构的核心其实只有一句话：<strong>把“一次大请求”拆成“多次小请求”，让堆里的临时对象随方法栈出栈而自然释放</strong>。OkHttp 的连接池、try-with-resources、分批循环，是 Java 后端做高吞吐图像 AI 推理时最实用的三件套。</p>]]>
